title: Films To Watch (Or Not) With Your Family

description: Matthew Socey speaks with All IN host Matt Pelsor about his new show and all shows named All IN or All In. They discuss the film The Art of Self Defense plus films to watch and not watch with our families. Matthew also replays his first chat with Chef Robert Irvine, who will be in Muncie next week.
